"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642782359,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"IU-i-kF5nIZeBKXPWO_cSASnNMdP7uhPELSxN4FLde0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x72bb5D221d810FD00605011AdD17356D63daD184\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"kzndXIRqs3eJJ-J6nlOS1CEOkS8bAc--Se54iOQmlto\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ekaSWpsG7gFht_xqKFd-iK4LMX3ERiymKCUZ9BMOexg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"gycmJgS09glGVx83vNVE0hfdDQP7GomwXKbnc1rIqdFdta2vjCupTEr9HVOws1I34Iiz4cCOK4FbOf7D-_zBOg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x15a14a07d70158023fb541174176a1bbe26bd24692506bd375f5b390339aac4d06d937c8e4c92952e6fa8b8cd52e72e2e06681ffb70556b5e5c1184869eb31921c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"kzndXIRqs3eJJ-J6nlOS1CEOkS8bAc--Se54iOQmlto\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ekaSWpsG7gFht_xqKFd-iK4LMX3ERiymKCUZ9BMOexg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi